## Regression Testing
1. UI Consistency:
   - All components render correctly
   - Styles remain unchanged
   - Responsive behavior maintained

2. API Compatibility:
   - All endpoints return expected formats
   - Error handling remains consistent
   - Backward compatibility maintained
